snippet.title: Our Time Has Come - Amber Lily WILD
snippet.description:
Family,
It is my joy to share this with you.
Please share this video & pre-Order WILD now!
www.amberlilymusic.com

OUR TIME HAS COME.
To be bright and bold,
Creative and courageous.
To be voices of Love & Justice,
To stand up for Life.

It is time to remember the beauty of our planet.
It is time to reclaim our place as artists, lovers, and family members.
While storms rage, and the future of our place on Earth is unclear,
Give us songs to sing together.
Give us art so we may gracefully navigate the chaos.
Give us family so we may know the strength of solidarity.

It is time to inspire all the voices of Love in this world!
I share music to bring HOPE & INSPIRATION.

My full length album WILD is available Aug 31,
with 10 songs to inspire the hearts of many.
Pre-order now & I will send you this full length song.

Thank you to @Kauai Visual Arts @Adam Harris & @Tubby Love for creating this video with me! Everything we do is a team effort.
I am SO excited to be releasing this record with @Come To Life!

Love,
Amber Lily
